{"tid":936783,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"老娘的草根飯堂 - 照燒牛小排丼配溫泉蛋","createTime":"2018-12-11T04:58:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T12:25:36.000Z","uid":30742,"like":50,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"27d0748176b4a4c36b9a01783d055b23b91b7f4f","tid":936783,"uid":30742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:58:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3fyrRsP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3fyrRsP.jpg&h=125bdac0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_hJtOypbPHU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_hJtOypbPHU&d=HBUYAvvS2hiLONQlwd7QIJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=73261ed5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_hJtOypbPHU</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個係之前做左一次！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為放工極速煮就咩都無拍<br />\n但原來好多人都有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我之後斷斷續續做左幾次<br />\n發現都係用梁九記既牛小排最正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n牛脂均勻豐富，size切出黎都剛剛好<br />\n所以上星期有時間入大埔行轉就再入貨拍片<br />\n<br />\n加埋粒溫泉蛋同照燒汁係完美！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖文食譜 <a href=\"https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/12/teriyaki-steak-donburi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.com%2F2018%2F12%2Fteriyaki-steak-donburi.html&d=HBUYAvvS2hiLONQlwd7QIJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=52465968\" target=\"_blank\">https://oldlady0914.blogspot.com/2018/12/teriyaki-steak-donburi.html</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁 : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foldladycanteen%2F&d=HBUYAvvS2hiLONQlwd7QIJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=05c35a23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oldladycanteen/</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_oldlady_%2F&d=HBUYAvvS2hiLONQlwd7QIJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=8604a054\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/_oldlady_/</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Foldlady0914.blogspot.hk%2F&d=HBUYAvvS2hiLONQlwd7QIJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=70bb1562\" target=\"_blank\">http://oldlady0914.blogspot.hk/</a>"},{"pid":"cb4b50b76bec2d6612fd518ae2f48782096ae318","tid":936783,"uid":114271,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789a0dc11a3e2f06fadf2930bffa037c2cedbd71","tid":936783,"uid":4494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:59:51.000Z","msg":"老娘老娘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78fb8e59dbdd2e2a28766f1f0172dec45396da33","tid":936783,"uid":47910,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T05:00:38.000Z","msg":"留名遲d煮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"034a2fd6fde1b4b32b0b52b0d95807c94a0d9640","tid":936783,"uid":30742,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"789a0dc11a3e2f06fadf2930bffa037c2cedbd71","tid":936783,"uid":4494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T04:59:51.000Z","msg